In a video that went viral, Spur bully Nico "Mr Muscle" Viljoen repeatedly threatened Mabuya with violence, aggressively grabbed a girl who allegedly hit his child, and rattled a table. And this while they were there for a kiddies' party.Spur has banned this bully from its outlets but his actions have surely left a bitter taste in the mouths of racism-hating South Africans.